        "release_notes": {
            "en-US": "Each action included calendar task tree refresh.\nThis version would be kept as it is, if problem would not occur.\n\nTo reviewers of Mozilla Thunderbird add-ons and users.\n\nI request update this addon which is precious for me. \nAbout 620 times have been tried to execute these actions.\nAnd, Thank you for approval and use of this addon. \n\nThank you."
        },
