    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "<b>Please, use browserAction to put it at toolbartoolbar or menubar.</b>\n<b>Please, put browserAction at mail toolbar, when not using button.</b>\n<b>Soon, if calendaring APIs completed, I will update this program^^.</b> \nExecuted well.\n\n praise Stephen Kim Sou-hwan.\n\n<b>[Notes]\nI removed a upside taskview in this version, because the functionality was not high.\nI know you are inconvenient using browserAction button. As of the present, TaskviewLayout button can be positioned at task toolbar(2) in a form of the past instead of browserAction. I consider whether I wait future browserAction upgrade or I return it to the past form which is possible in my technical scope now.</b>\n\n<b>Horizontal level of taskview</b>\nAdjust horizontal level, <b>before clicking any button of browserAction.</b>\nIf so, during TaskviewLayout running time, horizontal level can be adjusted to that point.",
        "ko": "문서를 읽을 때는 올려서 보세요.\n목록을 읽을 때는 내리고 보세요.\n행이 많은 문장은 세로로 보세요.\n세로로 크게 보시려면, 투데이 페인을 닫으세요.\n\n김수환 추기경님을 기리며.\n\n개발자 황성호."
